m nome diferente, você pode adicionar uma barra vertical \"","line":7},{"title":" mas com um ponto de exclamação antes:\n\n![[[Nome da Nota","target":"mas com um ponto de exclamação antes:\n\n![[[Nome da Nota","line":34},{"title":"[Nome da Nota#Titulo","target":"[Nome da Nota#Titulo","line":45,"embedded":true},{"title":"[Nome da Nota#  \n```\n\nE o próprio Obsidian irá te sugerir algumas opções para você embedar, incorporar, um pedaço da sua nota.\n\n**Exemplo de Título:**\n\n**Quando digito o nome da nota e coloco # aparece esta opção:**\n\n![","target":"https://api-club-file.cb.hotmart.com/public/v5/files/0617b6c4-e3b0-412f-8746-29e1a0738cd7","line":53,"embedded":true},{"title":"Nome da Nota#^","target":"Nome da Nota#^","line":82,"embedded":true},{"title":"021 - Seja um Otimista Racional#^f08c08","target":"021 - Seja um Otimista Racional#^f08c08","line":90,"embedded":true},{"title":"Documentação Obsidian","target":"https://help.obsidian.md","line":122}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[6,8],[10,13],[15,25],[33,37],[44,46],[51,54],[80,83],[88,91],[120,123],[134,137],[140,144],[151,155],[160,162]],"last_embed":{"hash":"xuyi8o","at":1770170907033}},"smart_blocks:Tutorial Obsidian/Aprendendo Obsidian/Topicos/9. Criando Links.md####Links Internos": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06855312,-0.01778616,0.07520428,-0.02875558,-0.02775658,-0.02128559,-0.0728374,0.04682934,-0.039581,0.00214095,0.00923216,-0.07489154,-0.00694652,0.03700772,0.02145994,-0.00482257,-0.01363018,0.07190312,-0.00743704,0.03788344,0.12984787,-0.0214283,0.02095828,-0.02967412,-0.01327846,0.02125362,0.03873139,-0.02281176,-0.00896668,-0.16575488,-0.0046611,0.01703469,-0.07135478,-0.00644331,-0.07121444,-0.00306166,-0.01712799,-0.04632154,-0.01395325,0.04935564,0.0409101,0.01451032,-0.05342249,0.00557776,-0.05840239,-0.06469931,0.02154996,-0.0290388,0.02574815,0.003873,-0.03327742,0.00923971,0.0032758,-0.0085889,-0.00647943,0.068753,0.08735676,0.01672898,0.